SUMMARY:Dinner at Amadeo's before they move!
DESCRIPTION:Raleigh & Triangle Activities Meetup Group\nAs you may have he
 ard\, Amadeo's Italian Restaurant will be moving after 60 years at their W
 estern Blvd location\, so let's enjoy one of Raleigh's finest establishmen
 ts before it moves!\n\nIF you can join us for dinner at 7pm on Sunday Marc
 h 29th\, please let me know.\n\n[Mecca Market](https://www.google.com/sear
 ch?sca_esv=af8dce034db735b1&rlz=1C1RINU_enUS1192US1192&sxsrf=ANbL-n7zojeHj
