 T8nMsYQ8G0oAHoECEAQAQ)\n[Address](https://www.google.com/search?sca_esv=af
 8dce034db735b1&rlz=1C1RINU_enUS1192US1192&sxsrf=ANbL-n7zojeHjvGpf0aaASWS3B
 E87ut3XA:1774191308686&q=amedeo%27s+italian+restaurant+address&ludocid=446
 8893948553396858&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwiU2d7V4bOTAxV848kDHT8nMsYQ6BN6BAg2EAI): 3
 905 Western Blvd\, Raleigh\, NC 27606\nPhone: [(919) 851-0473](https://www
 .google.com/search?gs_ssp=eJzj4tZP1zcsyUkqyzFLMWC0UjWosLBMTE4zTUq0TEoxTU4y
 NLQyqDBONTBJMjZNNTczSzIwMk_0Yk_MTUxJzS8GAC9TEic&q=amadeos&rlz=1C1RINU_enUS
 1192US1192&oq=amadeo&gs_lcrp=EgZjaHJvbWUqEggBEC4YJxivARjHARiABBiKBTIPCAAQI
 xgnGOMCGIAEGIoFMhIIARAuGCcYrwEYxwEYgAQYigUyDAgCEEUYORixAxiABDIHCAMQABiABDI
 HCAQQLhiABDIHCAUQLhiABDIOCAYQLhgKGAsYsQMYgAQyBggHEEUYPNIBCDQ1OTVqMGo3qAIAs
