SUMMARY:Salsa & Bachata Night @ Komana Brewery in Cary 
DESCRIPTION:Raleigh & Triangle Activities Meetup Group\nNo foolin'\, join 
 us on April 1st for a fun night of Salsa & Latin dancing! The only trick i
 s how fast the night flies.\n\nCome early\, doors open at 7:15 for a meet 
 and greet mixer then join in on the dance lessons!\n\n💃 Salsa & Bachata
  Lesson | 7:30–8:30 PM\nBeginner-friendly • No partner needed\n\n🎁 
 A chance to win free door prize give-a-ways after the lessons\n🕺 Social
  Dancing | 8:30–11:30 PM\n\n🎧 DJ Giovanni spinning Salsa\, Bachata & 
 Latin hits\n\n🎂 Celebrating April Birthdays\n\n🔥 Drink specials all 
 night!\n\n🍻 Dance • Drink • Connect\n\n💲 $15 pre-pay at salsa4li
 fe.com\nSave $5 use discount code meetup5\n\n📍 KōMANA Brewing Co.\n102
 0 Ryan Rd\, Cary\, NC\n\n🚗 Free parking | 18+ to party\, 21+ to drink
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/raleigh-triangle-activities/events/31
 3937117/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260325T025748Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260325T025748Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
